      "en": "a short, congenial fellow.",
      "zh": "一位身材矮小、和藹可親的男子。",
      "note": "DESC"
    },
    {
      "offset": 43,
      "len": 36,
      "en": "\"Welcome to the Blue Bottle Tavern.\"",
      "zh": "「歡迎光臨藍瓶酒館。」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 84,
      "len": 33,
      "en": "\"Anything else I can do for you?\"",
      "zh": "「還有什麼吾能為汝效勞的？」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 125,
      "len": 18,
      "en": "\"I'm Rob Frasier.\"",
      "zh": "「吾是羅伯·弗雷澤。」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 165,
      "len": 32,
      "en": "\"I brew Frasier's Folly myself.\"",
      "zh": "「弗雷澤之愚醇乃吾親自釀造。」",
      "note": "glossary: Frasier's Folly→弗雷澤之愚醇"
    },
    {
      "offset": 200,
      "len": 38,
      "en": "\"'Tis a very popular @ale hereabouts.\"",
      "zh": "「此乃本地最受歡迎之@麥酒。」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 248,
      "len": 52,
      "en": "\"Which, @mead, @wine, @bread, baked @brie, or @ale?\"",
      "zh": "「要@蜂蜜酒、@葡萄酒、@麵包、烘烤@布利乳酪，還是@麥酒？」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 310,
      "len": 82,
      "en": "\"I sell @mead, @wine, @bread, baked @brie, and the house brew, @Frasier's @Folly.\"",
      "zh": "「吾售賣@蜂蜜酒、@葡萄酒、@麵包、烘烤@布利乳酪，以及本店自釀的@弗雷澤之@愚醇。」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 487,
      "len": 16,
      "en": "\"See you later.\"",
      "zh": "「後會有期。」",
      "note": "bye"
    },
    {
      "offset": 508,
      "len": 29,
      "en": "\"I can't help you with that.\"",
      "zh": "「此事吾幫不上汝。」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 627,
      "len": 16,
      "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
      "zh": "「汝等哪一位？」",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "offset": 653,
      "len": 16,
      "en": "\"Suit yourself.\"",
      "zh": "「悉聽尊便。」",
      "note": "decline response"
    },
